===Proper noun===
'''[[Estonian]] [[Soviet Socialist Republic|SSR]]'''
# Estonian Soviet Socialist Republic, the name for the [[Estonia|Republic of Estonia]] while under the rule of the [[Soviet Union]] (1940-1991, name changed in 1990).

